HB1760
1 Coordination Division under § 26-26-407; or
2 (C) Valuation of producing mineral rights in accordance
3 with the directions and methods established by the division under § 26-26-
4 1110; or
5 (D) County assessor's determination whether a property
6 qualifies for the homestead property tax relief provided for a person who is
7 disabled or a person sixty-five (65) years of age or older under Arkansas
8 Constitution, Amendment 79, and § 26-26-1124.
9
10 SECTION 2. Arkansas Code § 26-27-317(a), concerning applications for
11 an adjustment of a property assessment to a county equalization board, is
12 amended to add an additional subdivision to read as follows:
13 (4) A petition for a claim under subdivision (a)(3) of this
14 section shall be filed with the county court of the county in which the
15 property is located, which has exclusive original jurisdiction under Arkansas
16 Constitution, Article 7, § 28, and § 14-14-1105.
